title: Policy9130(1)
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The Board shall hold an organizational meeting in the month following the last election of its members held in the member towns in any calendar year at which time the Board shall elect from its membership a Chairperson, a Vice-Chairperson, a Secretary, a Treasurer and any other officer deemed necessary. In the case of a tie vote in the balloting for any officer, such tie shall be broken by lot.
